original_title: Royal Visit of the Duke and Duchess of Cornwall and York to New Zealand
overview: The Duke and Duchess of Cornwall and York travelled to New Zealand in 1901 to thank New Zealanders for their contribution to the Boer War.  Only a short fragment remains of a much longer film.

production_companies.name: Limelight Department of the Salvation Army, Melbourne
